Project Deviant
Notes on the meetings held up to 03/05/2017

As suggested by Wil, the group decided on what features to include and what not
to include:

DOs
Nonlinear gameplay
Level and inventory diversity
Break the fourth wall
Tragedy elements

DON'Ts
Guns
Open ending
Grinding

Guidelines:

Art:
2D art
Intense soundtrack

Gameplay:
"80 minutes" gameplay
Blank slate protagonist
Adventure genre
Fixed camera

Target public:
Adults with little time to spend on games (PC)

Ideas for story development:
Mastermind trope
Protagonist blackmailed
Reverse psychology

Team division:
Barone, Gabriel - art, story
Jo√£o, Guilherme - implementation
